parameters.name: ClusterId
parameters.description: The ID of the ASK cluster.

parameters.name: ClusterName
parameters.description: The name of the cluster. This parameter is required if the ClusterType parameter is set to ecs.

parameters.name: ClusterType
parameters.description:
The cluster type.

Valid values:

*   ecs: ECS
*   one: ACK One
*   ask: ASK
*   pro: Container Monitoring Pro

parameters.name: GrafanaInstanceId
parameters.description: The ID of the managed Grafana workspace that is associated with the cluster. If you set this parameter to free or leave this parameter empty, the cluster is associated with a shared Grafana workspace.

parameters.name: SecurityGroupId
parameters.description: The ID of the security group to which the cluster belongs.

parameters.name: VSwitchId
parameters.description: The ID of the vSwitch that is used by the cluster.

parameters.name: VpcId
parameters.description: The virtual private cloud (VPC) where the cluster resides.
